'''卡尔·理查德·乌斯'''（{{lang-en|'''Carl Richard Woese'''}}{{Notetag|其姓氏{{Lang|en|'''Woese'''}}（{{IPA-en|woʊz}}）除音譯成「烏斯」外，也譯作'''沃斯'''、'''霍斯'''、'''伍斯'''、'''渥西'''、'''渥易斯'''等}}，{{bd|1928年|7月15日|2012年|12月30日}}），生于[[锡拉丘兹_(纽约州)|纽约州锡拉丘兹]]，美国[[微生物学|微生物学]]家和[[生物物理学|生物物理学]]家。乌斯因在1977年由对[[16S_核糖体RNA|16S 核糖体RNA]][[系统发生学|系统发生]][[生物分類學|分類學]]分析定义了[[古菌|古菌]]（生物的一个新的[[域_(生物)|域]]）而知名，这个由乌斯开创的[[16S_核糖体RNA|16S 核糖体RNA]]技术彻底改变了微生物学的学科<ref name="Woese_1990">{{cite journal | last1 = Woese | first1 = Carl R. | last2 = Kandler | first2 = O | last3 = Wheelis | first3 = M | title = Towards a natural system of organisms: proposal for the domains Archaea, Bacteria, and Eucarya | url = http://www.pnas.org/cgi/reprint/87/12/4576 | journal = Proc Natl Acad Sci USA | volume = 87 | issue = 12 | pages = 4576–9 | year = 1990 | pmid = 2112744 | doi = 10.1073/pnas.87.12.4576 | pmc = 54159 | bibcode = 1990PNAS...87.4576W | access-date = 2014-10-25 | archive-date = 2008-06-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080627233102/http://www.pnas.org/cgi/reprint/87/12/4576 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="woese1978">{{cite journal | last1 = Woese | first1 = C.R. | last2 = Magrum | first2 = L.J. | last3 = Fox | first3 = G.E. | title = Archaebacteria | journal = J Mol Evol | volume = 11 | issue = 3 | pages = 245–51 | year = 1978 | pmid = 691075 | doi = 10.1007/BF01734485}}</ref><ref name="woese1977">{{cite journal|pages=5088–5090|title=Phylogenetic structure of the prokaryotic domain: The primary kingdoms|volume=74|issue=11|date=1977-11-01|journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences|url=http://www.pnas.org/cgi/doi/10.1073/pnas.74.11.5088|accessdate=2018-04-02|author=Carl R. Woese, George E. Fox|doi=10.1073/pnas.74.11.5088|archive-date=2020-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200609233450/https://dx.doi.org/cgi/doi/10.1073/pnas.74.11.5088|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他还是[[RNA世界学说|RNA世界学说]]的创始人，虽然当时该理论还不叫那个名字<ref name="woese1967">{{Cite book | publisher = Harper & Row | last = Woese | first = Carl | title = The Genetic Code: the Molecular basis for Genetic Expression | url = https://archive.org/details/geneticcodemolec00woes | location = New York | year = 1967 }}</ref>。

